🔌 Complete Connection Table
🟦 ESP32 ↔ MPU6050
| MPU6050 Pin | Connect To ESP32 |
| ----------- | ---------------- |
| VCC         | 3.3V             |
| GND         | GND              |
| SDA         | GPIO 21          |
| SCL         | GPIO 22          |
| AD0         | GND              |

🟨 Servo 1 (BASE Servo — GPIO 18)
| Servo Wire             | Connection      |
| ---------------------- | --------------- |
| Signal (Yellow/Orange) | GPIO 18         |
| VCC (Red)              | 5V Power Module |
| GND (Brown/Black)      | Common GND      |


🟨 Servo 2 (TOP Servo — GPIO 19)
| Servo Wire             | Connection      |
| ---------------------- | --------------- |
| Signal (Yellow/Orange) | GPIO 19         |
| VCC (Red)              | 5V Power Module |
| GND (Brown/Black)      | Common GND      |


⚡ Power Module
| Power Module Pin | Connect To                                    |
| ---------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| 5V Rail          | Both Servo Red Wires                          |
| GND Rail         | Both Servo Ground Wires + ESP32 GND + MPU GND |

🔴 Common Ground (VERY IMPORTANT)
All of these connect together:
Ground Connections
ESP32 GND
MPU6050 GND
Servo 1 GND
Servo 2 GND
Power Module GND

👉 One shared common ground.

🔋 100µF Capacitor Connection
Connect capacitor across servo power rails:
| Capacitor Leg | Connect To |
| ------------- | ---------- |
| Long leg (+)  | 5V rail    |
| Short leg (-) | GND rail   |

📍Place it near where servo power wires connect.

| Function   | ESP32 GPIO |
| ---------- | ---------- |
| MPU SDA    | 21         |
| MPU SCL    | 22         |
| Base Servo | 18         |
| Top Servo  | 19         |
